IMPORTANT - PRINTER TEST PAGE

There is a certificate at the end of the quiz that you will be required to PRINT. This allows you to print a test page to ensure you are able to print the certificate.

 

1.        Click on the "Print Test Page" button below, and a new window will appear with a test page of information, and will request to print (with a "pop-up" computer dialog box).

2.        If a "pop-up" computer dialog box does not appear, you may have to select the "Print" function from your computer menu

3.        Print the test page, and verify your printer is operating properly.

4.        After the printed test page is sucessful, close the test page window.

5.        Advance to the CATC Test by using the "next page" green button below.
